Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Einstein Discovery allows you to Define Your Target Outcome, Prepare Data for Analysis, Create and Manage Models.

To use Text Clustering in Einstein Discovery:

* Select a variable with unstructured data (e.g. comments)
* Click Text Clustering from the Transform dropdown menu
* Train Model and review identified keyword clusters

This reduces unstructured data to its top keywords, revealing hidden insights and improving decision making.
title: Text Clustering for Analyzing Unstructured Data
